data.description: Move in ready rambler available now in the Sunday Lake Community-Enjoy private beach & boat access for low annual dues! This one level home features hardwood floors & a great layout. Open concept kitchen & dining area with a sliding glass door to an oversized entertainment deck. Spacious living room with a cozy a gas fireplace. The large primary bedroom includes additional space for an office, fitness room or nursery. Primary suite includes two closets,+ an en suite bathroom & shower. Located in the hallway is a full bathroom & the two additional bedrooms, side by side. Spread out in your nice sized lot with room to play & garden. Brand new tank less water heater recently installed. Make this home yours just in time for the Winter Holiday!
